@startuml Cake_Store_Context_Diagram
!define RECTANGLE class

skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle awesome

title Cake Store System - Context Diagram

' Actors
actor "Guest" as Guest
actor "Registered User" as RegUser
actor "Administrator" as Admin

' System
rectangle "Cake Store System" as System {
}

' Guest Interactions
Guest --> System : View products
Guest --> System : Search products
Guest --> System : Register
Guest --> System : Login

' Registered User Interactions
RegUser --> System : Place order
RegUser --> System : View order history
RegUser --> System : Write review
RegUser --> System : View products
RegUser --> System : Search products

' Administrator Interactions
Admin --> System : Manage users
Admin --> System : Manage products
Admin --> System : Manage categories
Admin --> System : Manage orders
Admin --> System : Manage reviews

note right of Guest
  Unauthenticated visitor
  Can browse and register
end note

note right of RegUser
  Authenticated customer
  Can make purchases and reviews
end note

note right of Admin
  System administrator
  Full management privileges
end note

note bottom of System
  Backend API handling:
  - Product catalog
  - User authentication
  - Order processing
  - Review management
  - Admin operations
end note

@enduml
